Description:
This subdirectory is reserved for dependencies that are part of the upstream `chromium` repository.
Sourced from https://source.chromium.org/chromium/chromium/src/+/main:components/variations/proto/devtools/.
The Revision is the chromium revision these have been taken from.

To update these dependencies, run this from the root of the `devtools-frontend` repository:

```sh
scripts/deps/roll_deps.py /path/to/chromium/src .
```

